msgid "GMMA 趋势结构"
msgstr "GMMA Trend Structure"

msgid ""
"短中长期 EMA 组构成 GMMA 结构，实时呈现线束收敛 / 发散，让「趋势方向 + 趋势强度」一眼可见，而不是只看单根 K 线的情绪波动。"
msgstr ""
"Short, mid, and long EMAs form the GMMA stack, visualizing "
"convergence/divergence so you see direction + strength at a glance instead "
"of single-candle noise."

msgid "趋势 + 动量双重过滤"
msgstr "Trend + Momentum Double Filters"

msgid "结合 Supertrend、ADX+DI、多周期动量与偏移分布等信号，主动回避震荡区间，尽量减少无效开仓和频繁“打脸”的来回反向。"
msgstr ""
"Supertrend, ADX+DI, multi-timeframe momentum, and deviation distributions "
"filter out chop to avoid useless trades and constant whipsaws."

msgid "波动与成交量控制"
msgstr "Volatility & Volume Control"

msgid "利用 ATR 比例、波动率上限与成交量过滤，识别极端波动与流动性陷阱，为实盘中的滑点、爆针和假突破预留安全缓冲。"
msgstr ""
"ATR ratios, volatility caps, and volume filters spot extreme swings and "
"liquidity traps, buffering against slippage spikes and fakeouts."

msgid "多层级入场逻辑"
msgstr "Multi-Layer Entry Logic"

msgid ""
"从 NEW-TREND（新趋势起爆）、GMMA-CROSS（多均线成束突破），到 TREND-RET（趋势回踩二次进场），分层布局，而不是“一脚踩死”。"
msgstr ""
"Layered entries from NEW-TREND ignition, GMMA-CROSS bundle breakouts, to "
"TREND-RET pullback re-entries so you don't go all-in at once."

msgid "实盘级出场与风控"
msgstr "Production-Grade Exits & Risk Controls"

msgid ""
"ATR 动态止损 + ATR 尾随止盈，配合 Supertrend "
"反转、布林极端与持仓时效管理，在「保住盈利」和「让利润奔跑」之间做平衡，而不是只盯单一止损价位。"
msgstr ""
"ATR dynamic stops plus trailing takes, paired with Supertrend flips, "
"Bollinger extremes, and position-duration rules to balance locking gains vs "
"letting profits run."

msgid "DynamicStakeController"
msgstr "DynamicStakeController"

msgid "根据行情状态与风险评分，动态调整仓位和子账户权重，控制同向暴露，让策略不仅“看得对”，还“下得稳”，避免一波行情把账户拖垮。"
msgstr ""
"Adjusts position size and sub-account weights per market state and risk "
"score to control correlated exposure so the strategy trades confidently "
"without blowing up."

msgid "突破监控（Breakout Radar）"
msgstr "Breakout Radar"

msgid "针对主流 USDT 永续合约，持续监控关键区间的向上 / 向下突破："
msgstr ""
"Continuously scans key zones on major USDT perpetuals for upside/downside "
"breakouts:"

msgid "多周期窗口（如 24 根 K 线）突破检测"
msgstr "Multi-timeframe (e.g., 24-bar) breakout detection"

msgid "BREAKOUT_UP / BREAKOUT_DOWN 精简列表输出"
msgstr "Concise BREAKOUT_UP / BREAKOUT_DOWN lists"

msgid "配合 GMMA 结构过滤假突破、追高与砸盘"
msgstr "GMMA filters remove fakeouts, FOMO highs, and rug pulls"

msgid "适合用来做候选标的池、重点关注列表以及盘中机会雷达。"
msgstr ""
"Great for building watchlists, focus shortlists, and intraday opportunity "
"radars."

msgid "市场评分（Market Scoring）"
msgstr "Market Scoring"

msgid "将行情“压缩”为可读的多空评分，而不是一堆杂乱的 K 线："
msgstr "Compresses chaotic charts into readable bull/bear scores:"

msgid "2h / 4h / 12h 多周期组合多头 / 空头得分"
msgstr "2h / 4h / 12h composite bull/bear scores"

msgid "给出一句话级别建议：偏多 / 偏空 / 中性观望"
msgstr "One-line guidance: bullish / bearish / neutral wait"

msgid "支持接入交易系统作为仓位权重与方向参考"
msgstr ""
"Integrates with trade systems as position-weighting and direction inputs"

msgid "先看市场整体体温，再决定个别币种如何出手。"
msgstr ""
"Gauge overall market temperature before acting on specific instruments."

msgid "策略信号（Strategy Signals）"
msgstr "Strategy Signals"

msgid "基于 TIDAL 的多因子引擎输出可直接执行的策略信号："
msgstr "TIDAL's multi-factor engine emits execution-ready signals:"

msgid "GMMA-BULL / GMMA-BEAR 结构变化提示"
msgstr "GMMA-BULL / GMMA-BEAR structure changes"

msgid "EL / ES / TREND-RET 等入场级别多空信号"
msgstr "EL / ES / TREND-RET long/short entries"

msgid "配合 ATR 止损、尾随止盈与趋势反转型出场提醒"
msgstr "Bundled with ATR stops, trailing TP, and trend-reversal exits"

msgid "从“看懂趋势”到“下得出手”，把方向判断和执行动作统一在一套逻辑里。"
msgstr ""
"Bridges \"understand trend\" to \"execute\" with unified direction + action "
"logic."

